dfischer.proxysniffer

Class PageBreakActionHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Dictionary<K,V>
      • java.util.Hashtable
        • dfischer.proxysniffer.PageBreakActionHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map

    public class PageBreakActionHandler
extends java.util.Hashtable
    Handles a collection of different actions, based and combined on/with one page break. NOTE: THIS CLASS IS REFERENCED BY A SINGLE PAGE BREAK DEFINITION. YOU MUST MAKE A LOOP OVER ALL PAGE BREAKS TO CATCH ALL INSTANCES!
    See Also:
    HttpPageBreak, Serialized Form
